metadata.name: Behind The Curtains
metadata.description:
Get close to what keeps you away.
As you get closer, you realize that everything is fine as long as you are a slave to the pretense.
Refer to your heart, everything is there.
Split whatever is needed.
Reveal the truth, the truth hidden behind the chest.
Be aware that the end is the beginning.
End the darkness for the light to begin.

Original Music By Ehsan EON
